The Korean Military Museum has a good collection, which is located in a relatively biased position and near the University of Qingxi. It mainly records the patriotic generals who resisted the Japanese army during the Korean period, and some famous generals in modern Korea. The most notable thing is the collection of weapons, aircraft, tanks and artillery.
Some history of the development of the South Korean military was introduced, and there were many weapons displays.
There are historical events, Korean military figures exhibition, passers-by can go to have a look
The Korean Military Museum was designed for military personnel. There is a service home for military personnel. Many memorials of war can also be seen. The logistical support of the army is good.
The Korean Military Museum is a very unique place, where the military culture is very rich, many military exhibits are worth seeing.
It's very interesting and attractive to see the name. The Military Museum attracts you to see what's on display inside.
If you're a military fan, you might as well check it out. There's still a lot of information here, but I'm not interested in it.
